\subtree{
\title{Core Insight}
\p{Skills are not static knowledge. They are:}

\ol{
\li{\strong{WORLD-GENERATING}: Each skill generates a local world model for its domain}
\li{\strong{SELF-IMPROVISING}: Skills learn from observations via ε-machine updates  }
\li{\strong{MEMORIES}: Crystallized patterns of successful action that persist and evolve}
}

\p{The sufficiency triad forms a closed \strong{autopoietic loop}:}

\pre{\startverb
dynamic-sufficiency (-1) ⊗ skill-dispatch (0) ⊗ skill-installer (+1) = 0 ✓
\stopverb}
}

\subtree{
\title{Variational Bound on Action}
