\li{\strong{max-fanout-gadget} FANS OUT: Maximizes parallel action (upper bound)}
}

\p{Together they form a variational bound ensuring both safety and maximum parallelism.}

\blockquote{*"The ε-machine is the minimal model sufficient to statistically reproduce the observed data."* — Crutchfield & Young, Santa Fe Institute}

